  "context": "Yoga studios have spread fast across Hong Kong in the last decade, especially through Central, Sheung Wan and Wan Chai, often filling converted industrial units with big windows. Instruction is usually bilingual, but knowing the Cantonese pose cues helps you actually follow along instead of just copying your neighbour.",
